### About

National statistics for Romania.

### Access

PDF files from statistical yearbook from 2007 are available for download under each topic:

 * <http://www.insse.ro/cms/rw/pages/index.en.do>

### Data

Topics include:

  * Geography, meteorology and environment
  * Population
  * Labour market
  * Population income, expenditure and consumption
  * Dwellings and public utilities
  * Social protection and assistance
  * Health
  * Education
  * Culture and sport
  * Prices
  * National accounts
  * Investments and tangible fixed assets
  * Research-development and innovation
  * Agriculture and sylviculture
  * Enterprise activity
  * Industry and construction
  * Transport, post and telecommunications
  * Foreign trade
  * Domestic trade and market services
  * Tourism
  * Finances
  * Justice
  * International statistics 

### Openness

Not open. Page footer says:

> Reproducing the content of this website, completely or partly, in original or modified, as well as its storage in a retrieval system, or transmitted, in any form and by any means are forbidden without the written permission of the National Institute of Statistics.
